{"tid":1233720,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"真心有疑問","createTime":"2019-06-16T20:43:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T22:39:48.000Z","uid":209620,"like":76,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"a7d71d176d70869247c05b4aa7b235ca8fcae796","tid":1233720,"uid":209620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T20:43:57.000Z","msg":"第一<br />\n經過2014同612大家佔領同衝擊立法會得知既結果係好易比啲狗圍住黎打。2014證明左佔領真係無用佢而加玩翻由鳩你佔既心態，時間耐左社會就會分化，唔係一擊即中，612有二讀所以圍立會都正常呀，但今晚圍立會有咩意思先，入面又無人、又無會開，所以班狗無防線，要圍到幾時，點解唔去禮賓府唱詩歌搵林奠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二<br />\n69個日103萬人但林奠唔聽所以先有612，暗中呢段期間係比時間大家養精神，部署好，有心理準備衝，有傳媒同外界比壓力，出師有名。今日200萬人響應遊行都引起好大迴響，今日既新聞稿正如69既時候咁，又助攻比多次機會大家去衝，但會唔會係部署下再衝，而唔係處於一個環境險峻，大家開始質疑大家係米鬼又盛時候去佔一個無人既法會，真係好易比敵人一下收皮。<br />\n<br />\n預左比人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6d3f73efab3ca2fdcb193a5dd7be51e6bb55a8f","tid":1233720,"uid":209620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T20:46:14.000Z","msg":"有無人同我講下一步係點"},{"pid":"3bb9ea8ea8dde1b64da5283d0dd12acf58e033bd","tid":1233720,"uid":209620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T20:46:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7fab70d3074133a7cdc4076ae187762d34349b0","tid":1233720,"uid":209620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T20:47:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f9c9d082bbfd3c8cf5de5a38957d148aea3e5d6","tid":1233720,"uid":209620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T20:48:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc6528e709b7d24096b3231baa2c7c071896dac1","tid":1233720,"uid":209620,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T20:49:05.000Z","msg":"快撚啲答我點解"},{"pid":"4bc75c294d6174ebdf3cbcd2fb446f0609a714c0","tid":1233720,"uid":16431